---
import PageLayout from "../layouts/PageLayout.astro";
---

<PageLayout title="JoÃ£o's Hyprland Dots" icon="https://github.com/retrozinndev.png">

    <div class="content top">
        <h1>Retrozinn's Hyprland Dots</h1>
        <p>My personal customization for <b>Hyprland</b>.</p>
        <img src="https://github.com/retrozinndev/Hyprland-Dots/blob/ryo/repo/screenshot_tools.png?raw=true" width="60%" alt="Hyprland Dots Screenshot">

        <span class="author">Made with <i>Care</i>, by <a href="https://github.com/retrozinndev">retrozinndev</a></span>
    </div>

    <ul class="content">
        <li class="right">
            <img src="https://github.com/retrozinndev/Hyprland-Dots/blob/ryo/repo/shots/showoff.png?raw=true" alt="Usage Screenshot">

            <h1>Dynamic colors</h1>
            <p>These Hyprland dotfiles are compatible with Pywal's Dynamic colors. There's a script that when you change wallpapers, colors will be refreshed and hot-reloaded automaticaly via the script.</p>
        </li>

        <li class="left">
            <h1>Tools</h1>
            <p>For the status bar, Waybar, for notification daemon and control center, it's SwayNC, for Application Launcher and stdin(dmenu-like) I use Anyrun, for the logout, shutdown, restart and lock buttons it's Wlogout, and, for clipboard management, it's used wl-copy, cliphist and Anyrun's menu.</p>
            <img src="https://github.com/retrozinndev/Hyprland-Dots/blob/ryo/repo/screenshot_usage.png?raw=true" alt="Tools Screenshot">
        </li>
    </ul>
</PageLayout>

<style lang="scss">
    
    b {
        font-weight: 400;
    }

    img {
        border-radius: 8px;
    }

    .content {
        display: block;
        padding: 12px;
    }

    .content > h1, .content > h2, .content > h3 {
        font-weight: 700;
    }

    .content.top {
        background: rgb(20, 16, 20);
        margin-inline: 6px;
        border-radius: 12px;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 3rem;
    }

    .content.top > img {
        margin-block: 1.6em;
    }

    .content.top > p {
        font-weight: 300;
    }

    .author {
        display: block;
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: 18px;
    }

    ul.content {
        width: 100%;
        height: max-content;
    }

    ul.content > li {
        display: block;
        list-style: none;
        height: max-content;
    }

    .content .right, .content .left {
        display: block;

        padding: 16px 6em;
        text-align: center;
    } 

    .content > * > h1 {
        font-size: 2.5em;
    }

    .content > * > p {
        font-size: 1.12em;
        font-weight: 400;
    }

    .content > * > img {
        display: inline-flex;
        width: 40%;
        height: 40%;
    }

    .content > .right img {
        float: left;
        margin-right: 12px;
    } 

    .content > .left > img {
        float: right;
        margin-left: 12px;
    }
    
</style>
